---
title: Chinese Black Bean Chicken with Water Chestnuts, Mushrooms, and Five-Spice
description: Chinese five-spice is a pungent mix of star anise, cloves, cinnamon, Sichuan peppercorns, and fennel. Anise-forward and slightly sweet, it perfumes the dish with its unique aroma. Black bean sauce is a staple of Chinese cooking; our version utilizes black beans rather than fermented soy beans to bring a variety of textures to the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55b91d48fd2cb9b7748b4567.jpg
